{"tid":1936022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（無事喇 開返喇）港鐵即日起局部開放羅湖站方便市民往沙嶺掃墓","createTime":"2020-03-21T03:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T03:44:31.000Z","uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2f00d0dd6dcefd7c9cbade923849d2054b7a23","tid":1936022,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"港鐵即日起局部開放羅湖站方便市民往沙嶺掃墓<br />\n2020-03-21 HKT 11:0<br />\n<br />\n東鐵由即日至4月19日，部分列車會來往羅湖站。（港鐵網頁截圖）<br />\n東鐵由即日至4月19日，部分列車會來往羅湖站。（港鐵網頁截圖）<br />\n港鐵宣布，為方便市民前往沙嶺掃墓，即日起至4月19日，由頭班車起至晚上7時，東鐵綫部分列車會來往羅湖站。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，羅湖站會局部開放，但落馬洲站仍然關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515933-20200321.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515933-20200321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F5Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=403b7dcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515933-20200321.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2a606106\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515933-20200321.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8314fab78b517df771b9de4a0706cc7ca6e575c1","tid":1936022,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T03:44:31.000Z","msg":"要去拜山喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}